section.section:
This subsection does not apply to or affect the suspension of any license:
For failure to comply with the required security provisions of Title 17 of this article;
For failure to appear at a hearing as provided in Title 12, Subtitle 2 of this article;
For failure to obey a citation, as provided in Title 26 of this article;
For failure to pay a fine in accordance with the court's directive as provided in Title 27 of this article; or
For failure to pay child support, as provided in § 16-203 of this subtitle.
